Request computer setup:
```
cd /
edit startup.lua
delete gib.lua
shell.run("wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/svencan/elements/master/gib.lua gib.lua)
```

Then save, exit, and type `reboot`.

Turtle (hol) setup:
```
cd /
edit startup.lua
delete hol.lua
delete listener.lua
shell.run("wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/svencan/elements/master/hol.lua hol.lua)
shell.run("wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/svencan/elements/master/listener.lua listener.lua)
shell.run("listener 1")
```

Then save, exit, and type `reboot`.